# WillyBeat Preset v2
version: 2
name:    Glitchy IDM Skitter
genres:  Electronic, IDM, Glitch, Experimental, Digital, Skittering, Cerebral, Anxious, Art Rock, Indie Electronic, 2000s, Mid-tempo, Synth, Drum Machine, Underground
type:    Regular
